# 7. Best Practices Followed

* Never login directly as root.
* Always validate SSH configuration before restarting the SSH service.
* Follow the Principle of Least Privilege.
* Keep only required firewall ports open.
* Use password expiration policies.
* Review logs regularly.
* Backup configuration files before modification.

